{"tid":804289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(辱華案) 罵中國人「不配做人、思想低劣」　廈大助教被解雇","createTime":"2018-09-03T02:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T11:56:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8e7da362e378b531a9b7d469dde6ab35cd968a","tid":804289,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"大陸廈門大學歷史系助理教授周運中，日前以網名「東海道子」在微博上發表多篇貼文，批評中國人思想低劣、不配做人，廈門大學週六(1日)以「發表錯誤言論」等理由，決定將他解雇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/09/03/20180903090528-10f4aacf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F20180903090528-10f4aacf.jpg&h=a4dcde7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／翻攝自微博<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n助理教授周運中日前在微博發文，稱「中國人最高境界是說假話、做假帳、訂假合同，真是最劣等民族」、「中國科技比美國至少落後五千年，是思想落後、民性落後、制度落後」，更直言「中國人不配做人」，據了解，目前微博上已無法搜尋「東海道子」的帳號及發文。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2018/09/03/20180903090530-5ccd925a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F20180903090530-5ccd925a.jpg&h=c60f75f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／翻攝自微博<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此，廈門大學官網指出，周運中無視學院的教育幫助，在微博上多次發表錯誤言論，不但歪曲歷史事實，更逾越師德師風底線，在社會上造成極壞影響，與廈門大學教師的身份嚴重不符，因此校方決定，根據《廈門大學教師職務聘任條例》等相關規定，解除與周運中的聘用關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/985471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F985471&d=ndkQznoxMezB%2Fw7L1lA0CO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=ad0253cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/985471</a>"},{"pid":"f2c46d66204eb06e6a4dacb81fc5e4e66d2a13bc","tid":804289,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a697f0f4f88ab1c6f7ed1f553f9f118c42f05807","tid":804289,"uid":130563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"講真話的代價"},{"pid":"4bf07eae55c2aec2ce375da3da31606b9907c6a6","tid":804289,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:22:04.000Z","msg":"凡支那反對的人都係好人"},{"pid":"d677d6d02af92c170c77a20f12f5a6603b30f59f","tid":804289,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"比人捉左未？"},{"pid":"951ee821259a0d6f5470ed927e535d842b1d7ec9","tid":804289,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"So what?<br />\nSo辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a36875fbb2185a45c6fb7af08664d53d0fb580b","tid":804289,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:27:49.000Z","msg":"現代林語堂"},{"pid":"e9ab90d850abfdc26ead9e40f151c6c94a3cd6ae","tid":804289,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"講事實啫,  支那玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b184cb9525b9378cb6fe722e4a44f79d55c45bd3","tid":804289,"uid":64347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"講真話既下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f82ce35e648d8db47482eab82af01fa7cbfa8f9","tid":804289,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:42:01.000Z","msg":"你一醒就要死"},{"pid":"8fcdb51c07c5f90535850aae6d9192ad79a96898","tid":804289,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"你講真話，中國人聽到難受。<br />\n<br />\n中國人一唔高興就要人死嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}